SCHEDULER.DESCRIPTION: Scheduler for the process check workflows that has to run every 5 mins and update few tables or send out notifications.
SCHEDULER.NAME: DAILY_EVERY_5MIN

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This sequence is used to populate the RUID for TENANTNAME_DI_AUDIT_DETAILS table only.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: seq_TENANTNAME_DICL_AUDIT_DETAILS

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select sq.ruid, sq.uniquefilename, sq.sapcstagetablename, sq.sapcimportbatchname, max(case when sq.metrictypename like '%Valid%' then sq.metricelementvalue else null end) as validcount, max(case when sq.metrictypename like '%Error%' then sq.metricelementvalue else null end) as errorcount, max(case when sq.metrictypename like '%Xfer%' then sq.metricelementvalue else null end) as transfercount from (select aud.ruid, aud.uniquefilename, aud.sapcstagetablename, aud.sapcimportbatchname, prst.name prstagetypename, ssst.name ssstagetypename, mt.name metrictypename, me.value metricelementvalue from tenantname_dicl_audit aud join cs_plrun pr on aud.sapcimportbatchname = pr.batchname join cs_stagetype prst on pr.stagetypeseq = prst.stagetypeseq join cs_stagesummary ss on pr.pipelinerunseq = ss.pipelinerunseq and ss.removedate = pr.removedate join cs_stagetype ssst on ss.stagetypeseq = ssst.stagetypeseq join cs_metricelement me on ss.metricsummaryseq = me.metricsummaryseq join cs_metrictype mt on me.metrictypeseq = mt.metrictypeseq where aud.statusflag = 4 and pr.command = 'Import' and pr.status = 'Successful' and pr.removedate = to_date('1/1/2200','MM/DD/YYYY') and pr.pipelinerunseq = (select max(pipelinerunseq) from cs_plrun prmax where prmax.batchname = aud.sapcimportbatchname and prmax.removedate = to_date('1/1/2200','MM/DD/YYYY') and ((upper(aud.sapcstagetablename) = 'CS_STAGEPARTICIPANT' and upper(prmax.runparameters) like '%[STAGETABLES]PARTICIPANT%') or (upper(aud.sapcstagetablename) = 'CS_STAGEPOSITION' and upper(prmax.runparameters) like '%[STAGETABLES]POSITION%') or (upper(aud.sapcstagetablename) = 'CS_STAGETITLE' and upper(prmax.runparameters) like '%[STAGETABLES]TITLE%') or (upper(aud.sapcstagetablename) = 'CS_STAGEQUOTA' and upper(prmax.runparameters) like '%[STAGETABLES]QUOTA%') or (upper(aud.sapcstagetablename) = 'CS_STAGEGENERICCLASSIFIER' and upper(prmax.runparameters) like '%[STAGETABLES]GENERICCLASSIFIER%') or (upper(aud.sapcstagetablename) = 'CS_STAGEVARIABLEASSIGNMENT' and upper(prmax.runparameters) like '%[STAGETABLES]VARIABLEASSIGNMENT%') or (upper(aud.sapcstagetablename) = 'CS_STAGESALESTRANSACTION' and upper(prmax.runparameters) like '%[STAGETABLES]TRANSACTIONANDCREDIT%'))) and ((upper(aud.sapcstagetablename) = 'CS_STAGEPARTICIPANT' and upper(mt.name) like 'PARTICIPANT%') or (upper(aud.sapcstagetablename) = 'CS_STAGEPOSITION' and upper(mt.name) like 'POSITION%') or (upper(aud.sapcstagetablename) = 'CS_STAGETITLE' and upper(mt.name) like 'TITLE%') or (upper(aud.sapcstagetablename) = 'CS_STAGEQUOTA' and upper(mt.name) like 'QUOTA%') or (upper(aud.sapcstagetablename) = 'CS_STAGEGENERICCLASSIFIER' and upper(mt.name) like 'GENERICCLASSIFIER%') or (upper(aud.sapcstagetablename) = 'CS_STAGEVARIABLEASSIGNMENT' and upper(mt.name) like 'VARIABLEASSIGNMENT%') or (upper(aud.sapcstagetablename) = 'CS_STAGESALESTRANSACTION' and upper(mt.name) like 'SALESTRANSACTION%')) ) sq group by sq.ruid, sq.uniquefilename, sq.sapcstagetablename, sq.sapcimportbatchname

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select aud.uniquefilename, aud.sapcstagetablename, aud.sapcimportbatchname, md.messagekey as FIELDNAME, md.messagelevel||' '||md.description as VALIDATIONMESSAGE, pr.stoptime as VALIDATIONDATETIME, st.orderid, st.linenumber, st.sublinenumber, st.eventtypeid, case when msg.subcategory = 'Participant' then spar.payeeid when msg.subcategory = 'Position' then spos.payeeid else null end as payeeid, case when msg.subcategory = 'Position' then spos.positionname when msg.subcategory = 'Quota' then squota.positionname when msg.subcategory = 'Variable Assignment' then svara.assigneename else null end as positionname, stitle.name as titlename, squota.quotaname as quotaname, svara.variablename as variablename, sgenclass.classifierid as classifierid, case when msg.subcategory = 'Participant' then spar.effectivestartdate when msg.subcategory = 'Position' then spos.effectivestartdate when msg.subcategory = 'Title' then stitle.effectivestartdate when msg.subcategory = 'Quota' then squota.effectivestartdate when msg.subcategory = 'Variable Assignment' then svara.assigneedate when msg.subcategory = 'Generic Classifier' then sgenclass.effectivestartdate else null end as effectivestartdate, case when msg.subcategory = 'Participant' then spar.effectiveenddate when msg.subcategory = 'Position' then spos.effectiveenddate when msg.subcategory = 'Title' then stitle.effectiveenddate when msg.subcategory = 'Quota' then squota.effectiveenddate when msg.subcategory = 'Generic Classifier' then sgenclass.effectiveenddate else null end as effectiveenddate from tenantname_dicl_audit aud join cs_plrun pr on aud.sapcimportbatchname = pr.batchname join cs_messagelog ml on pr.pipelinerunseq = ml.sourceseq join cs_message msg on ml.messagelogseq = msg.messagelogseq join cs_messagedesc md on msg.messagekey = md.messagekey left outer join cs_stagesalestransaction st on msg.objectseq = st.stagesalestransactionseq+(101*281474976710656) left outer join cs_stageparticipant spar on msg.objectseq = spar.stageparticipantseq+(104* 281474976710656) left outer join cs_stageposition spos on msg.objectseq = spos.stagepositionseq+(105*281474976710656) left outer join cs_stagetitle stitle on msg.objectseq = stitle.stagetitleseq+(106*281474976710656) left outer join cs_stagequota squota on msg.objectseq = squota.stagequotaseq+(139*281474976710656) left outer join cs_stagevariableassignment svara on msg.objectseq = svara.stagevariableassignmentseq+(135*281474976710656) left outer join cs_stagegenericclassifier sgenclass on msg.objectseq = sgenclass.stagegenericclassifierseq+(118*281474976710656) where aud.statusflag = 4 and pr.command = 'Import' and pr.status = 'Successful' and pr.removedate = to_date('1/1/2200','MM/DD/YYYY') and pr.pipelinerunseq = (select max(pipelinerunseq) from cs_plrun prmax where prmax.batchname = aud.sapcimportbatchname and prmax.removedate = to_date('1/1/2200','MM/DD/YYYY') and prmax.command = 'Import' and prmax.status = 'Successful' and ((upper(aud.sapcstagetablename) = 'CS_STAGEPARTICIPANT' and upper(prmax.runparameters) like '%[STAGETABLES]PARTICIPANT%') or (upper(aud.sapcstagetablename) = 'CS_STAGEPOSITION' and upper(prmax.runparameters) like '%[STAGETABLES]POSITION%') or (upper(aud.sapcstagetablename) = 'CS_STAGETITLE' and upper(prmax.runparameters) like '%[STAGETABLES]TITLE%') or (upper(aud.sapcstagetablename) = 'CS_STAGEQUOTA' and upper(prmax.runparameters) like '%[STAGETABLES]QUOTA%') or (upper(aud.sapcstagetablename) = 'CS_STAGEGENERICCLASSIFIER' and upper(prmax.runparameters) like '%[STAGETABLES]GENERICCLASSIFIER%') or (upper(aud.sapcstagetablename) = 'CS_STAGEVARIABLEASSIGNMENT' and upper(prmax.runparameters) like '%[STAGETABLES]VARIABLEASSIGNMENT%') or (upper(aud.sapcstagetablename) = 'CS_STAGESALESTRANSACTION' and upper(prmax.runparameters) like '%[STAGETABLES]TRANSACTIONANDCREDIT%')))
